  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a bindsClaim reference to a Claim node that carries thorough prose justification but lacks a structured prov:wasDerivedFrom derivation link to any Evidence node, instantiating the W-EP-01 orphan-claim weakness.",
