      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA pump benchmark",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity magnitudes against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements from the FDA pump benchmark study at 2500 RPM and 4 L/min. Mean absolute error 6.3% of peak velocity; 92% of measurement locations within ±15% band.",
