    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing significant epistemic gaps. The primary hemolysis claim (bindsClaim) is considered supported by the body of computational and experimental work described in the claim statement, including mesh convergence studies, Monte Carlo UQ, and in-vitro comparisons. On the basis of the documented evidence narrative, the assessment team accepted the package pending resolution of the six not-assessed factors in a subsequent submission. The decision is accepted at this stage with the understanding that the not-assessed factors must be addressed before regulatory submission.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
  },
